task_description: Facing the building to your South (approx. 184°), estimate the height of the main building in front of you in meters. Answer with one number and a short rationale.

reason: Moving to the front-right position (move_id 1) will give me a new perspective to better view the full height of the target building, which is necessary for accurate estimation.
Based on typical mid-rise residential building dimensions, estimating 7 floors at 3 meters per floor gives a total height of 21 meters.
